    • testCreateHospitalStayCorrect

      @Test public void testCreateHospitalStayCorrect()
      This test checks if it is possible to create a HospitalStay object using the BasicDBService.createHospitalStay(Patient, Ward, Date) method. To pass the test, the return value of the method must not be null, the admission date, ward and patient must agree with the default values.
